<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Surveyor" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Surveyor,</orth> (<emph>survéyor;</emph> in <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.222" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 222</bibl> <emph>súrveyor</emph>), an overseer: <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.253" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 253</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.115" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.115" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 115</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.172" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.1.19" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 19</bibl>. == a measurer of land: <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 3, 53</bibl>.
